author: Associated Press
title: Fear grips Swedish soccer as virus delays start of season
description: Saturday was supposed to mark the beginning of a new Swedish soccer season, fuelled by the prospect of big broadcasting revenues from a new domestic TV deal and expectations of another tight title race to match last year’s dramatic finale
